From 1f36ef0bc0d3945438314d01ceb4d4a2eac8b101 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Christian Hewitt <christianshewitt@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Jan 2023 07:31:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 07/39] WIP: media: tuners: add MxL603/MxL608 tuner drivers

MxL608 is often paired with the second generation AVL6862/AVL6762
demod chips. MxL603 is often paired with the older AVL6211 demod
chip. Analysis of the original separate drivers shows them to be
identical bar a single register value difference (reg 0xD5: 0x05
vs 0x04 in the DVB-C table). Add support for both tuners with all
shared logic refactored into a common module.

Signed-off-by: Christian Hewitt <christianshewitt@gmail.com>
---
 drivers/media/tuners/Kconfig         |   23 +
 drivers/media/tuners/Makefile        |    3 +
 drivers/media/tuners/mxl603.c        |   40 +
 drivers/media/tuners/mxl603.h        |   68 ++
 drivers/media/tuners/mxl608.c        |   41 +
